[
  {
    "start": 6.64,
    "end": 8.16,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Hello, I'm Dr."
  },
  {
    "start": 8.16,
    "end": 9.2,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Jill."
  },
  {
    "start": 9.2,
    "end": 13.04,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Welcome to Let's Learn English with Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 13.04,
    "end": 14.32,
    "text": "**DrJill:** {Yesterday|昨日}"
  },
  {
    "start": 14.2,
    "end": 18.2,
    "text": "**DrJill:** I {hurt|痛める/傷つける}/ˈhɜːrt/ my {hand|手}/hænd/, fixing my {car|車}."
  },
  {
    "start": 18.2,
    "end": 20.92,
    "text": "**DrJill:** It hurt a lot."
  },
  {
    "start": 20.92,
    "end": 24.439,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Today we {talk|話す}/tɔːk/ about {accidents|事故/偶発的な出来事}."
  },
  {
    "start": 24.24,
    "end": 27.6,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Like {falling|落ちる} down or {hitting|打つ} your head."
  },
  {
    "start": 28.4,
    "end": 30.8,
    "text": "**DrJill:** We all have {accidents|事故/偶発的な出来事}."
  },
  {
    "start": 30.8,
    "end": 33.68,
    "text": "**DrJill:** And some {accidents|事故/偶発的な出来事} hurt."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.96,
    "end": 36.36,
    "text": "**DrJill:** So let's visit Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 36.36,
    "end": 38.04,
    "text": "**DrJill:** She {answers|答える} the question."
  },
  {
    "start": 38.04,
    "end": 38.76,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Ow!"
  },
  {
    "start": 38.76,
    "end": 40.52,
    "text": "**DrJill:** What hurts?"
  },
  {
    "start": 41.08,
    "end": 42.04,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hi there!"
  },
  {
    "start": 42.36,
    "end": 46.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** {Daisy|人名} is {stuck|立ち往生した/はまっている} on the {garage|車庫} roof."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.36,
    "end": 49.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** I am helping her down."
  },
  {
    "start": 49.64,
    "end": 53.48,
    "text": "**Daisy:** And you are taking a long time."
  },
  {
    "start": 54.6,
    "end": 57.64,
    "text": "**Anna:** I am being {careful|注意深い}."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.64,
    "end": 58.92,
    "text": "**Anna:** Hi, Max."
  },
  {
    "start": 58.92,
    "end": 62.12,
    "text": "**Max:** Anna, I have the question for today."
  },
  {
    "start": 62.12,
    "end": 62.839,
    "text": "**Anna:** Great!"
  },
  {
    "start": 62.839,
    "end": 64.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** What is the question?"
  },
  {
    "start": 64.439,
    "end": 66.039,
    "text": "**Max:** What hurts?"
  },
  {
    "start": 66.039,
    "end": 67.719,
    "text": "**Anna:** What hurts?"
  },
  {
    "start": 67.719,
    "end": 72.759,
    "text": "**Anna:** What sorry, Daisy"
  },
  {
    "start": 73.54,
    "end": 74.98,
    "text": "**Anna:** What hurts?"
  },
  {
    "start": 75.3,
    "end": 76.74,
    "text": "**Anna:** {Everything|すべて}."
  },
  {
    "start": 76.74,
    "end": 81.46,
    "text": "**Daisy:** {Everything|すべて} hurts."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.46,
    "end": 86.58,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Some {hurts|痛み} are small, but some {hurts|痛み} can hurt a lot."
  },
  {
    "start": 86.62,
    "end": 90.86,
    "text": "**DrJill:** The word {hurt|痛める/傷つける|/hɜːrt/|I hurt my finger.} is a noun and a verb."
  },
  {
    "start": 90.86,
    "end": 95.9,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Sometimes in English we use {get|～する/～になる|/ɡet/|I get happy.} with the word hurt."
  },
  {
    "start": 95.82,
    "end": 97.18,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Like this."
  },
  {
    "start": 97.18,
    "end": 99.98,
    "text": "**DrJill:** You can get {hurt|怪我する|/hɜːrt/|Be careful not to get hurt.} in an accident."
  },
  {
    "start": 99.98,
    "end": 103.9,
    "text": "**DrJill:** If it happened in the past, use GOT."
  },
  {
    "start": 103.9,
    "end": 106.46,
    "text": "**DrJill:** I got hurt yesterday"
  },
  {
    "start": 107.259,
    "end": 110.06,
    "text": "**DrJill:** And now let's hear from some friends."
  },
  {
    "start": 110.06,
    "end": 112.619,
    "text": "**DrJill:** They talk about getting hurt."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.619,
    "end": 117.02,
    "text": "**Students:** Once I {hurt|痛めた|/hɜːrt/|I hurt my leg.} my back {surfing|サーフィンをする|/ˈsɜːrfɪŋ/|I love surfing.} in the ocean."
  },
  {
    "start": 117.76,
    "end": 123.68,
    "text": "**Students:** I hurt my arm {riding|乗って|/ˈraɪdɪŋ/|I enjoy riding my bike.} my bike."
  },
  {
    "start": 123.68,
    "end": 127.76,
    "text": "**Students:** I hurt my knee in a {soccer|サッカー|/ˈsɑːkər/|I play soccer every weekend.} league."
  },
  {
    "start": 127.76,
    "end": 130.24,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Feel better soon, friends."
  },
  {
    "start": 130.14,
    "end": 135.579,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Diamond says is a {fun|楽しい|/fʌn/|This game is fun.} game to practice actions and body parts."
  },
  {
    "start": 135.579,
    "end": 140.54,
    "text": "**DrJill:** To play, one person is a leader and says an action."
  },
  {
    "start": 140.32,
    "end": 144.08,
    "text": "**DrJill:** The other people in the game do the action."
  },
  {
    "start": 144.08,
    "end": 147.6,
    "text": "**DrJill:** But only if they hear Simon says"
  },
  {
    "start": 148.36,
    "end": 153.48,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Anna's new game is Simon Says Super."
  },
  {
    "start": 153.48,
    "end": 156.28,
    "text": "**DrJill:** That sounds {super|とても/超|/ˈsuːpər/|That's a super idea.} fun!"
  },
  {
    "start": 156.96,
    "end": 160,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is my new game."
  },
  {
    "start": 160,
    "end": 162.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** Simon says super."
  },
  {
    "start": 162.72,
    "end": 164.8,
    "text": "**Anna:** The game gives actions"
  },
  {
    "start": 165.12,
    "end": 168.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** I listen for Simon says."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.56,
    "end": 170.72,
    "text": "**Anna:** Then I do the action."
  },
  {
    "start": 170.72,
    "end": 173.28,
    "text": "**Anna:** I {set|セットする/準備する|/set/|I set the table for dinner.} the game too fast."
  },
  {
    "start": 173.48,
    "end": 175.96,
    "text": "**Anna:** and human."
  },
  {
    "start": 175.96,
    "end": 182.76,
    "text": "**Anna:** It uses human body parts like head, nose."
  },
  {
    "start": 182.98,
    "end": 192.02,
    "text": "**Anna:** Ears, eyes, arms, hands, legs, knees."
  },
  {
    "start": 192.08,
    "end": 193.52,
    "text": "**Anna:** Toes."
  },
  {
    "start": 193.52,
    "end": 194.32,
    "text": "**Anna:** Feet."
  },
  {
    "start": 194.88,
    "end": 197.2,
    "text": "**Anna:** Anna, I want to play."
  },
  {
    "start": 197.52,
    "end": 200.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** {Daisy|デイジー（女性名）}, you are a {flower|花}。"
  },
  {
    "start": 200.24,
    "end": 202.32,
    "text": "**Anna:** You can play next."
  },
  {
    "start": 202.32,
    "end": 204.32,
    "text": "**Anna:** But please be {careful|注意深い/気をつける}."
  },
  {
    "start": 204.32,
    "end": 206.88,
    "text": "**Anna:** Do not {touch|触れる} the game."
  },
  {
    "start": 206.96,
    "end": 208.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** Be careful?"
  },
  {
    "start": 208.54,
    "end": 210.86,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Anna, you {dropped|落とした} me."
  },
  {
    "start": 210.86,
    "end": 211.9,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Remember?"
  },
  {
    "start": 212.14,
    "end": 213.02,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Yeah."
  },
  {
    "start": 213.02,
    "end": 215.5,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Anna said many {body parts|体の部位}."
  },
  {
    "start": 215.5,
    "end": 217.42,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Did you {hear|聞く} them all?"
  },
  {
    "start": 217.44,
    "end": 228.959,
    "text": "**DrJill:** She said, Head, nose, ears, eyes, arms, hands, legs, knees, toes, feet"
  },
  {
    "start": 229.52,
    "end": 233.44,
    "text": "**DrJill:** The word {said|言った} is the past tense of say."
  },
  {
    "start": 233.44,
    "end": 235.52,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Now let's go back to Anna."
  },
  {
    "start": 235.52,
    "end": 237.84,
    "text": "**DrJill:** She plays Simon says"
  },
  {
    "start": 238.34,
    "end": 243.94,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Super Let's play Hi, I am Simon."
  },
  {
    "start": 243.94,
    "end": 246.34,
    "text": "**Students:** Simon says {touch|触れる} your nose"
  },
  {
    "start": 246.32,
    "end": 249.52,
    "text": "**Students:** Simon says, {clap|拍手する} your hands."
  },
  {
    "start": 249.52,
    "end": 251.28,
    "text": "**Students:** This is easy."
  },
  {
    "start": 251.52,
    "end": 253.6,
    "text": "**Daisy:** This is too easy."
  },
  {
    "start": 253.6,
    "end": 256.32,
    "text": "**Daisy:** Let's {set|設定する} it on faster."
  },
  {
    "start": 256.32,
    "end": 258.239,
    "text": "**Anna:** Simon says, {grab|つかむ} your arm."
  },
  {
    "start": 258.239,
    "end": 259.84,
    "text": "**Anna:** Simon says, {hit|叩く} your head."
  },
  {
    "start": 259.84,
    "end": 260.48,
    "text": "**Anna:** Simon says,"
  },
  {
    "start": 261.959,
    "end": 263.56,
    "text": "**Anna:** This is {harder|より難しい}."
  },
  {
    "start": 263.56,
    "end": 266.68,
    "text": "**Anna:** Daisy, please stop the game."
  },
  {
    "start": 266.68,
    "end": 267.88,
    "text": "**Daisy:** What, Anna?"
  },
  {
    "start": 268.04,
    "end": 270.12,
    "text": "**Daisy:** She said {fastest|最も速い}."
  },
  {
    "start": 273.88,
    "end": 275.8,
    "text": "**Daisy:** Anna, are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "start": 276.32,
    "end": 278.88,
    "text": "**Daisy:** BB, I think B."
  },
  {
    "start": 278.96,
    "end": 280.4,
    "text": "**Daisy:** She's head."
  },
  {
    "start": 282.16,
    "end": 287.04,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Now you can {explain|説明する/伝える|/ɪkˈspleɪn/|Can you explain this problem?} in English the next time you get {hurt|怪我する/傷つく|/hɜːrt/|I got hurt playing soccer.}"
  },
  {
    "start": 286.96,
    "end": 292.56,
    "text": "**DrJill:** Hopefully the {hurt|痛み/怪我} is small and you feel better soon."
  },
  {
    "start": 292.56,
    "end": 296.8,
    "text": "**DrJill:** See you next time on Let's Learn English with Anna!"
  }
]
